My personal site

To run local:
  docker build -t site:latest .
  docker run --rm -v $PWD:/site -p 1313:1313 --name wl.wtf site

Generating HTML files:
  docker exec wl.wtf hugo

Writing:
  * New page:
    - hugo new path/to/file.md

  * LaTeX:
    - create inline symbols putting LaTeX between single $
    - create symbols putting LaTeX between double $$
